{"tid":1423024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史教訓]要一隊軍隊幫助人民 只有兩個方法","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:45:11.000Z","uid":128869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99fc44e1cfeb6903b3a6b66f8b93bb7b62f68143","tid":1423024,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"一係上級支持人民 <br />\n一係呢隊軍隊不停打輸/知道自己會打輸<br />\n<br />\n所以人民嘅意志必須要表現出<br />\n1. 廣泛民意反對軍隊 並有決心長期對抗<br />\n2. 以頻繁嘅遊擊及定期嘅遊行令軍隊疲勞<br />\n3. 減少軍隊勝利 每一次軍隊成功鎮壓人民 都係軍隊嘅強心針<br />\n<br />\n人民同軍隊正面暴力對抗 吃虧嘅係人民<br />\n軍隊嘅惡夢 就係數量多同流動性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">俄羅斯帝國嘅革命之所以成功 就係對外戰爭接連失利 逃兵紛紛加入人民嘅陣營</span>"},{"pid":"3189e6d8831ebafa4502c2700a777751a119eef7","tid":1423024,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8060d5398c6b6f9e44919f2c07ccb8ee9aa5c9de","tid":1423024,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8037712ffb3f0daf998cfbd0e8d017116da47fe","tid":1423024,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"Summary: 麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370580a670b5fe8afe269edf2b52b61e129835fb","tid":1423024,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8037712ffb3f0daf998cfbd0e8d017116da47fe","tid":1423024,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"Summary: 麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cc2caeb24c672071475457408c326c7f6ced83","tid":1423024,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi